{"tid":1688434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我地一直做唔到臨時轉陣，人地重狗仲跟計劃走去送頭，只會係咁輸，而要變陣和理非嘅角色係關鍵","createTime":"2019-11-02T12:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T12:22:34.000Z","uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69752ee8e880bcf7f183c3bf893d6f629552702c","tid":1688434,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:07:21.000Z","msg":"Popo而家已經轉哂策略<br />\n以前示威係朝早等你行<br />\n夜晚和理非走左<br />\nPopo先出手<br />\n所以好多時可以搞到夜晚<br />\n而家係遊行未開始就搜身<br />\n嚇到啲人唔帶裝<br />\n一多人就理得你市民、和理非、定勇武<br />\n放左tg先<br />\n務求令你聚唔到人<br />\n遊行搞唔到<br />\n<br />\n以前我地會認為喺同一個地點<br />\n有好多人黎<br />\n可以留好長時間<br />\n就叫嗰日做得好<br />\n<br />\n如果仲抱住呢個mindset<br />\n就只會場場仗都輸！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地要改變贏嘅標準<br />\n變成睇廣度<br />\n越多地方開到花<br />\n就越叫成功<br />\n而家popo自己用tg封街<br />\n自己癱瘓一個地區<br />\n我已經覺得已經得到一個checkpoint<br />\n嗰日得到越多check point就贏得越大<br />\n<br />\n至於點樣可以得到多check point呢<br />\n連登仔一定要習得臨時改地方呢個技能<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臨時改地方有兩個困難<br />\n1） 示威者收唔到風<br />\n2） 新地方有狗巡邏搞到聚唔到人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要解決1，我地要培養隨時變陣嘅風氣<br />\n和理非都要裝連登同tg，下下都要睇蘋果A1先知去邊<br />\n太慢喇<br />\n示威者唔進化冇得打<br />\n<br />\n要解決2<br />\n一定係街坊行先<br />\n勇武後join<br />\n吹左雞<br />\n冇裝街坊就去靜坐摺紙又好，商場唱歌又好<br />\n一個人都可以坐喺度摺紙<br />\n摺摺下越黎越多人<br />\n務求低風險集合<br />\n狗搜身都搜唔到啲咩嗰隻<br />\n勇武匿埋先<br />\n千祈唔好成班勇武黑衣人聚集送頭<br />\n大家伺機待動<br />\n聚到街坊就有行動<br />\n聚唔到就唔好出動<br />\n<br />\n大家進化好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d733b0ed66e42140aa0a3f7227b50fbcc9e0da1f","tid":1688434,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02676eb69ebb33fe3f15121302d76b017142ec68","tid":1688434,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21ca91fd6c5294b62a275f6acc8e4d6719877d8","tid":1688434,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:10:15.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5920f209f69914d30f0c561b4fb0816fa95740b7","tid":1688434,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}